                ><p><strong>Access the Voice Assistant:</strong </p><p>Simply navigate to the voice assistant feature on your Carbinox Blaze smartwatch by selecting it from the main menu.</p><p></p><p><strong>Activate Voice Commands:</strong </p><p>Once in the voice assistant menu, tap the screen to speak.</p><p></p><p><strong>Send a Text Message:</strong </p><p>After activating the assistant, you can send a text message by saying the command, for example, &#8220;<strong>Send a text message to [name] saying [message].</strong>&#8221;</p><p></p><p><strong>Message Sent:</strong </p><p>The AI assistant will instantly pair with your smartphone and send the message as instructed.</p><p></p><p><strong>You can also make calls with the AI voice assistant. Just follow the same steps as the ones to send a message but instead, say "Call [name]".</strong></p
                ><p></p><p><strong>Important Disclaimer: </strong></p><p>While the AI voice assistant is highly responsive, it is also very sensitive. This means that in some cases, the message <strong>may not be delivered exactly as you intended.</strong> Always double-check your command to ensure it’s understood correctly. We recommend speaking clearly and confirming any important messages.</p></div
